          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Yes black devilry they are and claim the allegiance of the White Hand, whatever that is... I sent messengers to Isengard for Worm Tongue was long overdue. They came back bloodied and broken. If you are brave enough... I would reward you handsomely for clearing the blockade."
          }
        }
      },
